{"id":75604,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/比什么k线、均线、指标都更准确的股市信号/","date":"2010-05-31T08:19:53Z","modified":"2010-05-31T20:23:35Z","title":"老陈博客：比什么K线、均线、指标都更准确的股市信号","content":"<pre><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">一.进场的信号：</span></pre>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 1.炒股老头突发心肌梗塞，死在交易大厅里。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 2.贪官挪用公款炒股，无法归还，被逮捕。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 3.证券公司临时工领不到工资。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 4.私募的头子跳楼或者逃往国外。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 5.国家银行松动，乱放贷款。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">二、离场信号：</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n1.周小川讲话。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 2.尚福林要大力发展资本市场。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 3.股评家说机构给散户送钱。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 4.股仙曝光，股神出现。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 5.中石油狂拉指数。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">三、病态信号：</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n1.香港大佬来关心。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 2.经济学家来议论。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 3.罗杰斯，巴菲特，索罗斯来乱弹。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">4.新华社,人民日报来打气。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">说明：此三类信号极灵，百试不爽。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">信号一出现后，为安全期；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">信号二出现后,为危险期；</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">信号三出现后，为癌症末期。<br />\n</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 此类三信号远比什么K线、均线、指标都准确。</span></p>\n<p>See the original post:<br />\n<a title=\"比什么K线、均线、指标都更准确的股市信号\" href=\"http://laochen07.blog.sohu.com/152914153.html\" target=\"_blank\">比什么K线、均线、指标都更准确的股市信号</a></p>\n","author":853,"categories":[20534],"tags":[10940,10941]}